Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:40.07,Gen_Italics_top,Kenichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mis tratos con Mallow\Nme dieron 15 monedas de oro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.56,Cart_A_Tre,CARTEL,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\bord1.2\blur0.3\fs16\c&H434540&\3c&HCAC5BE&\pos(312,95)}Cargo completado
