Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.78,Gen_Italics,Kenichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ahora puedo comprar\Nla cabaña de madera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.77,Cart_A_Tre,CARTEL,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\an7\bord1.2\blur0.3\fs24\c&H424540&\3c&HD7D8CA&\pos(169,84)}Shangri-La
